<br>
1-Effect all of the skald songs by the correct percentage, so the dmg add is higher, the speed songs are higher, the regen song is higher, and the resist buffs are higher. If that seems to powerful then perhaps it should effect everything but the dmg chant (because the dmg chant buff would perhaps step on the toes of the uber-dmg song realm ability anyway). Needs to effect more then just speed for all the costs (with pre-reqs) IMHO..<br>
<br>
2-Not be limited by the caps.<br>
<br>
